payload.message:
Added a shared SectionWrapper and refactored every non-UI component to use it for consistent spacing and dark-mode styling.

- New wrapper exports consistent padding, container width, and dark background support with override hooks for outer/inner classes (`components/SectionWrapper.tsx:1`).
